      "description": "This E92 M3 is a prime example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era, featuring a linear power band and an 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a lightning-quick 7-speed M-DCT, while the chassis benefits from the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes treated rod bearings and reinforced throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and reciprocating assembly are track-ready. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise hydraulic steering feedback this platform is known for. Though the aesthetics reflect a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and thermal management are in excellent order.",
